title: Bucs-Cowboys preview; Super Bowl predictions; Brian Baumgartner
itunes:title: Bucs-Cowboys preview; Super Bowl predictions; Brian Baumgartner
description:
In the latest edition of the Good Morning Football Podcast, hosts Kay Adams, Michael Robinson Peter Schrager and Kyle Brandt dive into an in-depth preview of the Tampa Bay Buccaneers and Dallas Cowboys matchup; they also share their Super Bowl predictions and are joined by Brian Baumgartner from The Office!

The Good Morning Football Podcast is part of the NFL Podcast Network.
